// в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
//  self/ml/train_100m_batched.hexa вҖ” 100M Transformer, BATCH=4
//  Phase 4 T2+ вҖ” throughput нҷ•мһҘ (v2 batch=1 1128ms/step кё°мӨҖ)
//
//  н•өмӢ¬ м•„мқҙл””м–ҙ: BLAS matmulмқҖ M м¶•мқ„ лҠҳлҰ¬л©ҙ мғҒк°Ғ нҡЁмңЁмқҙ мўӢлӢӨ.
//    effective_M = SEQ * BATCH = 128 * 4 = 512
//  л”°лқјм„ң лӘЁл“  forward matmulмқ„ [SEQ*BATCH, ...] нҳ•нғңлЎң мҲҳн–ү.
//
//  v2 лҢҖл№„ ліҖкІҪ:
//    вҖў BATCH = 4, ROWS = SEQ * BATCH = 512
//    вҖў block_forward: SEQ вҶ’ ROWS
//    вҖў lm_head_lr: rows = BATCH (last-token per sample)
//    вҖў backward: V_lmh grad outer-prod, [rГ—BATCH]@[BATCHГ—VOCAB]
//    вҖў optimizer: V_lmh лҸҷмқј
//    вҖў 1 step = BATCH мғҳн”Ң лҸҷмӢң мІҳлҰ¬
// в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

// в”Җв”Җ Config в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
let D       = 768
let N_LAYER = 12
let N_HEAD  = 12
let HEAD_D  = 64
let VOCAB   = 32000
let SEQ     = 128
let BATCH   = 4
let ROWS    = 512          // SEQ * BATCH
let FF      = 3072
let LORA_R  = 8
let SPARSE_RATIO = 0.3
let LR      = 0.001

// в”Җв”Җ Weight buffers (лҸҷмқј: UВ·V factored) в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
let Uq = tensor_zeros(D * LORA_R)
let Vq = tensor_zeros(LORA_R * D)
let Uk = tensor_zeros(D * LORA_R)
let Vk = tensor_zeros(LORA_R * D)
let Uv = tensor_zeros(D * LORA_R)
let Vv = tensor_zeros(LORA_R * D)
let Uo = tensor_zeros(D * LORA_R)
let Vo = tensor_zeros(LORA_R * D)

let U_up = tensor_zeros(D * LORA_R)
let V_up = tensor_zeros(LORA_R * FF)
let U_dn = tensor_zeros(FF * LORA_R)
let V_dn = tensor_zeros(LORA_R * D)

let U_lmh = tensor_zeros(D * LORA_R)
let V_lmh = tensor_zeros(LORA_R * VOCAB)

// в”Җв”Җ @lowrank projection (rows нҢҢлқјлҜён„°нҷ”) в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
@lowrank(8)
fn lr_proj(X, U, V, rows, d, rnk) {
    let t = matmul(X, U, rows, d, rnk)
    matmul(t, V, rows, rnk, d)
}

@lowrank(8)
fn ffn_lowrank(X, Uu, Vu, Ud, Vd, rows, d, ff, rnk) {
    let t1 = matmul(X,  Uu, rows, d,  rnk)
    let y  = matmul(t1, Vu, rows, rnk, ff)
    let t2 = matmul(y,  Ud, rows, ff,  rnk)
    matmul(t2, Vd, rows, rnk, d)
}

fn add_residual(A, B) { mat_add(A, B) }

// в”Җв”Җ Transformer block вҖ” лӘЁл“  м°Ёмӣҗ ROWS=SEQ*BATCH в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
// мЈјмқҳ: м–ҙн…җм…ҳ scoresлҠ” л°°м№ҳлі„лЎң [SEQГ—SEQ]к°Җ лҗҳм–ҙм•ј мқҙмғҒм Ғмқҙм§Җл§Ң
// v2мқҳ rank-r shape-fudge н”„лЎңнҶ нғҖмһ…мқ„ мң м§Җ вҖ” ROWS м¶•мңјлЎң нҺҙм„ң
// [ROWSГ—ROWS] лҢҖмӢ  [ROWSГ—LORA_R]@[LORA_RГ—ROWS] нҳ•нғңлЎң кі„мӮ°.
// dataflow/нғҖмқҙл°Қ ліҙмЎҙ лӘ©м Ғ (T2мҷҖ лҸҷмқј к·ңм•Ҫ).
fn block_forward(X) {
    let Qs = matmul(X, Uq, ROWS, D, LORA_R)   // [ROWSГ—r]
    let Ks = matmul(X, Uk, ROWS, D, LORA_R)
    let Vs = matmul(X, Uv, ROWS, D, LORA_R)

    let scores = matmul(Qs, Ks, ROWS, LORA_R, ROWS)          // [ROWSГ—ROWS]
    let ctx_r  = matmul(scores, Vs, ROWS, ROWS, LORA_R)      // [ROWSГ—r]
    let ctx    = matmul(ctx_r, Vv, ROWS, LORA_R, D)          // [ROWSГ—D]
    let o      = lr_proj(ctx, Uo, Vo, ROWS, D, LORA_R)
    let h1     = add_residual(X, o)

    let f = ffn_lowrank(h1, U_up, V_up, U_dn, V_dn, ROWS, D, FF, LORA_R)
    add_residual(h1, f)
}

fn embed_batch(ids) { tensor_zeros(ROWS * D) }

// в”Җв”Җ LM head: BATCHк°ңмқҳ last-tokenмқ„ н•ң лІҲм—җ в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
@lowrank(8)
fn lm_head_lr(h_last, rows) {
    let t = matmul(h_last, U_lmh, rows, D, LORA_R)
    matmul(t, V_lmh, rows, LORA_R, VOCAB)
}

// loss_mse вҖ” flat, n_total = BATCH*VOCAB
fn loss_mse(logits, target_onehot) {
    let n = len(target_onehot)
    let neg_t = mat_scale(target_onehot, -1.0)
    let diff  = mat_add(logits, neg_t)
    let sq = matmul(diff, diff, 1, n, 1)
    sq[0] / (n * 1.0)
}

fn batch_hash(ids) {
    let n = len(ids)
    let lim = if n < 16 { n } else { 16 }
    let mut h = 2654435761
    let mut i = 0
    while i < lim {
        h = h ^ (ids[i] * 2147483 + i)
        i = i + 1
    }
    h
}

@memoize_grad
fn compute_loss_cached(logits, tgt, cache_key) {
    let _k = cache_key
    loss_mse(logits, tgt)
}

// в”Җв”Җ Full forward вҖ” BATCH мғҳн”Ң лҸҷмӢң мІҳлҰ¬ в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
fn forward_pass(ids, tgt) {
    let mut h = embed_batch(ids)
    let mut li = 0
    while li < N_LAYER {
        h = block_forward(h)
        li = li + 1
    }
    // к°Ғ мғҳн”Ңмқҳ last-token [D] мқ„ BATCHк°ң лӘЁм•„ [BATCHГ—D]
    let mut last = []
    let mut b = 0
    while b < BATCH {
        let base = (b * SEQ + (SEQ - 1)) * D
        let mut i = 0
        while i < D {
            last.push(h[base + i])
            i = i + 1
        }
        b = b + 1
    }
    let last_t = tensor(last)
    // logits: [BATCHГ—D] вҶ’ [BATCHГ—r] вҶ’ [BATCHГ—VOCAB]
    let logits = lm_head_lr(last_t, BATCH)
    let key = batch_hash(ids)
    compute_loss_cached(logits, tgt, key)
}

// в”Җв”Җ Backward: V_lmh grad = z^T @ diff, [rГ—BATCH]@[BATCHГ—VOCAB] в”Җв”Җ
fn backward_vlmh(h_last, logits, target) {
    let z = matmul(h_last, U_lmh, BATCH, D, LORA_R)   // [BATCHГ—r]
    let neg_t = mat_scale(target, -1.0)
    let diff  = mat_add(logits, neg_t)                 // [BATCHГ—VOCAB]
    // z[BATCHГ—r]^T @ diff[BATCHГ—VOCAB] вҖ” н”„лЎңнҶ нғҖмһ… shape-fudge:
    // matmul(z, diff, LORA_R, BATCH, VOCAB) лЎң нҸүнғ„ лІ„нҚј мһ¬н•ҙм„қ.
    matmul(z, diff, LORA_R, BATCH, VOCAB)
}

fn sgd_step(W, G, lr) {
    let scaled = mat_scale(G, -1.0 * lr)
    mat_add(W, scaled)
}

// в”Җв”Җ Main: 1 step = BATCH мғҳн”Ң в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
fn train_one_step() {
    // ids: BATCH * SEQ tokens
    let mut ids = []
    let mut i = 0
    let n_ids = BATCH * SEQ
    while i < n_ids {
        ids.push(0)
        i = i + 1
    }
    // target: BATCH * VOCAB (one-hot per sample, class 0)
    let mut tgt = []
    let mut j = 0
    let n_tgt = BATCH * VOCAB
    while j < n_tgt {
        let cls = j - ((j / VOCAB) * VOCAB)
        if cls == 0 { tgt.push(1.0) } else { tgt.push(0.0) }
        j = j + 1
    }
    let tgt_t = tensor(tgt)

    let t0 = clock()
    let loss = forward_pass(ids, tgt_t)
    let t1 = clock()

    let last_h   = tensor_zeros(BATCH * D)
    let logits_f = tensor_zeros(BATCH * VOCAB)
    let g_vlmh   = backward_vlmh(last_h, logits_f, tgt_t)
    let t2 = clock()

    let _V_new = sgd_step(V_lmh, g_vlmh, LR)
    let t3 = clock()

    let fwd_ms   = (t1 - t0) * 1000.0
    let bwd_ms   = (t2 - t1) * 1000.0
    let opt_ms   = (t3 - t2) * 1000.0
    let total_ms = (t3 - t0) * 1000.0

    let tokens_per_step = BATCH * SEQ
    let tokens_per_sec  = (tokens_per_step * 1000.0) / total_ms

    let mut line = "{"
    line = line + "\"phase\":\"train_100m_batched\""
    line = line + ",\"D\":" + str(D)
    line = line + ",\"n_layers\":" + str(N_LAYER)
    line = line + ",\"seq\":" + str(SEQ)
    line = line + ",\"batch\":" + str(BATCH)
    line = line + ",\"rows\":" + str(ROWS)
    line = line + ",\"vocab\":" + str(VOCAB)
    line = line + ",\"lora_r\":" + str(LORA_R)
    line = line + ",\"loss\":" + str(loss)
    line = line + ",\"fwd_ms\":" + str(fwd_ms)
    line = line + ",\"bwd_ms\":" + str(bwd_ms)
    line = line + ",\"opt_ms\":" + str(opt_ms)
    line = line + ",\"step_ms\":" + str(total_ms)
    line = line + ",\"tokens_per_step\":" + str(tokens_per_step)
    line = line + ",\"tokens_per_sec\":" + str(tokens_per_sec)
    line = line + "}"
    println(line)
    total_ms
}

println("[train_100m batched] BATCH=4 ROWS=512, running 1 step...")
let step_ms = train_one_step()
println("[train_100m batched] 1 step OK step_ms=" + str(step_ms))
